title: CutFill
description: A construction cost optimization tool that calculates the most efficient earthwork operations for site development.
fullDescription: CutFill is a specialized construction technology application developed during Week 5 of the Gauntlet AI intensive program. It helps construction professionals optimize earthwork operations by calculating the most cost-effective cut and fill strategies for site development. The tool analyzes topographical data, material costs, and equipment availability to provide optimal solutions that minimize both costs and environmental impact.
